item.description: 1.66.0 nightly # Unreleased Will be stable on: 15 December, 2022 Will branch from master on: 28 October, 2022 Stabilize duration_checked_float (merged 3 days ago) Don’t link to libresolv in libstd on Darwin (merged 3 days ago) Update libstd’s libc to 0.2.135 (to make libstd no longer pull in libiconv.dylib on Darwin) (merged 3 days ago) Change process spawning to inherit the parent’s signal mask by default (merged 6 days ago) Stabilize proc_macro::Span::source_text (merged 7 days ago) Stabilize map_first_last (merged 16 days ago) Stabilize half_open_range_patterns (merged 17 days ago) Fix #[derive(Default)] on a generic #[default] enum adding unnecessary Default bounds (merged 24 days ago) Make the c feature for compiler-builtins an explicit opt-in (merged 28 days ago) Stabilize #!

1.65.0 beta # Unreleased, branched from master Will be stable on: 3 November, 2022 Will branch from master on: 16 September, 2022 Stabilize let else (merged 40 days ago) Normalize struct field types in confirm_builtin_unsize_candidate (merged 42 days ago) Stabilize generic associated types (merged 44 days ago) Use niche-filling optimization even when multiple variants have data. (merged 49 days ago) Don’t duplicate file descriptors into stdio fds (merged 51 days ago) Uplift the let_underscore lints from clippy into rustc.
